OL,5, More than 300 ScotRail services have   
OL,6, been cancelled for the third Sunday in 
OL,7, a row due the ongoing shortage of      
OL,8, drivers.                               
OL,10,FThe disruption comes on the eve of     
OL,11,Fmajor timetable cuts which will see 700
OL,12,Fdaily services cut across the country. 
OL,14,FHundreds of trains have been cancelled 
OL,15,Fsince 8 May when many drivers opted not
OL,16,Fto work overtime.                      
OL,18,FDrivers' union Aslef is balloting      
OL,19,Fmembers for strike action after        
OL,20,Frejecting a 2.2% pay offer.            
